<h2 id="introducing-marketplace">Introducing the Marketplace</h2>

<p>We're excited to announce the launch of the Sonesse Marketplace — a curated collection of pre-built AI agents that developers can deploy into video meetings with minimal code.</p>

<p>The Marketplace is designed to solve a common challenge: while our Universal API gives you complete flexibility to build custom meeting experiences, many teams want to start with proven, production-ready agents and customise from there.</p>

<h2 id="whats-available">What's Available</h2>

<p>At launch, the Marketplace includes agents across several categories:</p>

<ul>
	<li><strong>Note Takers</strong> — AI-powered meeting summarisation with action item extraction</li>
	<li><strong>Real-Time Coaches</strong> — Live conversation analysis with contextual prompts</li>
	<li><strong>Digital Avatars</strong> — Photorealistic AI avatars for video calls</li>
	<li><strong>Voice Assistants</strong> — In-meeting AI assistants that respond to voice commands</li>
	<li><strong>Compliance Monitors</strong> — Real-time compliance checking for regulated industries</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="how-it-works">How It Works</h2>

<p>Each marketplace agent is a pre-configured combination of Sonesse capabilities — transcription, recording, real-time streaming, and bot management — packaged into a single deployable unit. You can deploy any agent with just a few lines of code and customise its behaviour through configuration.</p>

<h2 id="whats-next">What's Next</h2>

<p>We're working with partners to expand the Marketplace with specialised agents for healthcare, legal, education, and financial services. If you're interested in contributing an agent to the Marketplace, <a href="/demo/">get in touch</a>.</p>
